code: @Override public void setEnvironment(Environment environment) {     this.environment = (ConfigurableEnvironment) environment. }

@Override public VariableFetcher createFetcher(Object ctx, String name) {     VariableFetcher fetcher = super.createFetcher(ctx, name).     if (fetcher != null) {         return fetcher.     }     if (this.environment.containsProperty(name)) {         return this.propertyFetcher.     }     return null. }
@Override public Object get(Object ctx, String name) {     return MustacheEnvironmentCollector.this.environment.getProperty(name). }
